'''Bennay Waɛli''' d yiwen n umeɣnas n timunent n tmurt n [[Lzzayer]]. Illul deg tazwara n isegwasen n ɛcrin, yemmut deg usegwas n [[1957]]. 

D yiwen n umeɣnas daɣen n timuzɣa, n Lzzayer anda ilaq ad yilli umkan i Tmaziɣt. 

== Tameddurt-is == 

Bennay Waɛli illul deg taddart n Lǧemɛa n Sarriǧ deg lɛarc n [[At Frawsen]]. Asmi yella d amectuḥ, Bennay Waɛli yeffeɣ deg taddart. Iṛṛuḥ ar temnaṭ n Lzzayer am waṭṭas n Yeqbayliyen di tallit-nni. 

Yekcem ar [[Ukabar n Wegdud Azzayri]] (PPA) deg tezwara n isegwasen n rebɛin. Yuttusema-d d aqarru n ukabar-aggi deg tama n [[Ǧerǧer]]. 

Yettiki daɣen deg tarbaɛt yettwasenen s yisem n "Groupe d'étudiant de Ben Aknun", ar tama n [[Lḥusin At Aḥmed]], [[Ɛumar Usediq]], [[Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda]], Mbarek n At Mangellat. Tarbaɛt-aggi ad ttuɣal ad ttenaɣ ɣef umkan n Tmaziɣt deg Lzzayer.  D Bennay Waɛli ara yillin ɣef uqarruy n tarbaɛt-aggi.

Ɣef wanec-ta Bennay Waɛli yettwanɣa deg usegwas n 1957 deg taddart-is.

